      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad and Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, both together from Ibn Mahboub, from Ibn Raib, from a man, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> regarding a man who carried his slave upon an animal, so it trampled (someone). So he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The fine is upon his master’."
